"{\"uid\": \"sofokleous10.gr-2024-08-29-the-olympic-hotel-in-marousi-will-be-renewed-in-the-first-half-of-2025\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"In the first half of 2025, the \\\"Olympic\\\" hotel in Marousi, on Kifissia Avenue, is expected to be reopened by the REDS-SWOT duo, which leased the property owned by the Hellenic Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 50, \"end\": 57, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marousi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.675569759879132e-14, \"text\": \"Marousi\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marousi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marousi\"}, {\"begin\": 167, \"end\": 175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9999999988717718, \"rank\": 1.1267067279218605e-09, \"text\": \"Hellenic\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first half\", \"from\": 3, \"to\": 17}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Olympic\\\" hotel\", \"from\": 27, \"to\": 46}, {\"ngram\": \"Kifissia Avenue\", \"from\": 62, \"to\": 77}, {\"ngram\": \"the REDS-SWOT duo\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 126}, {\"ngram\": \"the property\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two sides are expected to proceed with a \\\"facelift\\\", amounting to about 3 million euros, of the property which was operating until last March as the 4-star unit \\\"Civitel Olympic\\\" by the Civitel group, aiming to create a fully modernized hotel unit, in an area that essentially has no significant hospitality infrastructure, while it is also ideal for business meetings/events due to the wider business center of Maroussi.\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marousi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.045353769275199e-17, \"text\": \"Maroussi\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \